[There is a very effective vaccine for the equines. Horse owners need to vaccinate immediately and to continue to use equine specific mosquito and fly repellents.

For more information regarding EEE, readers are encouraged to see the moderator's comments in ProMED-mail posting 20140614.2539697.

The state of Florida can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=2564100,4047.

Volusia and Brevard counties can be seen on the map at http://geology.com/county-map/florida-county-map.gif. - Mod.TG]
